text: Cottage Grove is an unincorporated community in Center Township, Union County, in the U.S. state of Indiana. ==History== A post office was established at Cottage Grove in 1848, and remained in operation until it was discontinued in 1951. ==Geography== Cottage Grove is located at . ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Union County, Indiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Indiana
